        <detaileddescription>
<para>Sets the interruption context for the calling thread. <parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>newctx</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>the interruption context to attach or NULL for none </para>
</parameterdescription>
